-- Real Madrid Beats Galatasaray in Champions League Quarterfinals
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2013-04-03T20:38:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-03/real-madrid-beats-galatasaray-in-champions-league-quarterfinals.html
Real  Madrid  beat Galatasaray 3-0 in
their Champions League soccer quarterfinal opener, as Malaga and
Borussia Dortmund drew 0-0.  Cristiano Ronaldo, Karim Benzema and Gonzalo Higuain scored
the goals in Real Madrid’s home victory.  Galatasaray and Dortmund will host the return matches in
the two-game series on April 9, with the winners advancing to
the semifinals of Europe’s elite club competition.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  